This folder encapsulates all local saliency functions bkN_SAL.m, where N={0 (blocks), 1(overlapping blocks), 2 (convoluted blocks)}, SAL={cov(ariance), var(iance), drg (dynamic range), ent(ropy)}. Precalculated files are available at deakin.edu.au/~mhossny/fusion

Feel free to use and distribute the code provided that the description in the .m functions is intact. Please refer to the papers listed below if you are using in your research. More details are documented in the matlab function.

[1] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S.; Creighton, D.; Bhatti, A, "Image fusion performance
metric based on mutual information and entropy driven quadtree decomposition," 
Electronics Letters, vol.46, no.18, pp.1266,1268, 2010. 
(doi: 10.1049/el.2010.1778)

[2] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S.; Creighton, D., "Comments on 'Information measure 
for performance of image fusion'," Electronics Letters , vol.44, no.18, 
pp. 1066-1067, 2008. (doi: 10.1049/el:20081754)

[3] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S., "Measuring the capacity of image fusion," Image 
Processing Theory, Tools and Applications (IPTA), IEEE International
Conference on, pp. 415-420, 2012. (doi:10.1109/IPTA.2012.6469548)

[4] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S.; Creighton, D., "An Evaluation Mechanism for Saliency 
Functions Used in Localized Image Fusion Quality Metrics," Computer Modelling and 
Simulation, International Conference on, pp. 407-415, 2012 (doi: 10.1109/UKSim.2012.63)

[5] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S.; Creighton, D., "Zero and infinity images in multi-scale
image fusion," Image Processing (ICIP), IEEE International Conference on, pp. 2181-2184,
2009. (doi: 10.1109/ICIP.2009.5413827)

[6] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S.; Creighton, D.; Bhatti, A; Hassan, M., "Image Fusion Metrics: 
Evolution in a Nutshell," Computer Modelling and Simulation, International Conference on, 
pp. 443-450, 2013. (doi: 10.1109/UKSim.2013.72)

[7] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S., "Image fusion algorithms and metrics duality index," Image
Processing (ICIP), 2009 16th IEEE International Conference on , vol., no., pp.2193,2196, 2009.
(doi: 10.1109/ICIP.2009.5413850)

[8] Hossny, M.; Nahavandi, S. & Creighton, D., "Feature-Based Image Fusion Quality Metrics,"
Lecture Notes on Computer Science, 2008, 5314, 469-478